data.text:
How can one download a year's worth of check images for a Wells Fargo checking account?

https://www.wellsfargo.com/biz/help/faqs/check-images/ describes a poor option of "go to Account Activity. Click the check icon next to the check you would like to see." This will be onerous for a full year's worth of checks.
